movies.title: MIB: Homens de Preto
movies.description: A police officer joins a secret organization that polices and monitors extraterrestrial interactions on Earth.

movies.title: MIB: Homens de Preto II
movies.description: Agent J is sent to find Agent K and restore his memory after the re-appearance of a case from K's past.

movies.title: MIB: Homens de Preto III
movies.description: Agent J travels in time to M.I.B.'s early days in 1969 to stop an alien from assassinating his friend Agent K and changing history.

movies.title: MIB: Homens de Preto - Internacional
movies.description: The Men in Black have always protected the Earth from the scum of the universe. In this new adventure, they tackle their biggest threat to date: a mole in the Men in Black organization.

movies.title: Coringa
movies.description: In Gotham City, mentally troubled comedian Arthur Fleck is disregarded and mistreated by society. He then embarks on a downward spiral of revolution and bloody crime. This path brings him face-to-face with his alter-ego: the Joker.

movies.title: Vingadores: Ultimato
movies.description: After the devastating events of Vingadores: Guerra Infinita (2018), the universe is in ruins. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers assemble once more in order to reverse Thanos' actions and restore balance to the universe.

movies.title: Capitã Marvel
movies.description: Carol Danvers becomes one of the universe's most powerful heroes when Earth is caught in the middle of a galactic war between two alien races.

movies.title: Shazam!
movies.description: A newly fostered young boy in search of his mother instead finds unexpected super powers and soon gains a powerful enemy.

movies.title: John Wick 3: Parabellum
movies.description: John Wick is on the run after killing a member of the international assassin's guild, and with a $14 million price tag on his head, he is the target of hit men and women everywhere.

movies.title: Avatar
movies.description: A paraplegic Marine dispatched to the moon Pandora on a unique mission becomes torn between following his orders and protecting the world he feels is his home.

movies.title: The Falcon and the Winter Soldier
movies.description: Following the events of 'Avengers: Endgame,' Sam Wilson/Falcon and Bucky Barnes/Winter Soldier team up in a global adventure that tests their abilities -- and their patience.
